<div class="news">
  <div class="top">
    <h3>News</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>THIS WEEKEND FREEFALL HIGHSCORE IS GOING TO BE AT THE CREATORS PROJECT NEW YORK EVENT</p>
    <p><a href="http://thecreatorsproject.com/events/the-creators-project-new-york-2011" target="_blank">The Creators Project: New York 2011</a></p>
